LeadFlow CRM — Setup Instructions
Overview
LeadFlow CRM is a client lead management dashboard with features including lead tracking, pipeline management, analytics, and real-time reporting. The application is a self-contained HTML file that runs entirely in the browser.

System Requirements
Requirement	Minimum
Browser	Chrome (latest), Firefox (latest), Edge (latest), Safari (latest)
Internet	Required for Google Fonts, Chart.js CDN (first load only)
Storage	No disk space requirement (runs in memory)
Installation Steps
Step 1: Save the File
Create a new file named LeadFlow-CRM.html on your computer

Copy the entire HTML code provided

Paste it into the file and save

Step 2: Open the Application
Double-click the LeadFlow-CRM.html file — it will open in your default web browser

OR Right-click → Open with → Choose your preferred browser

