Data Persistence
⚠️ Important: This is a demo application. All data is stored in browser memory only.

Leads are NOT saved between page refreshes or browser sessions

Reloading the page resets all data to the default demo leads

No database or backend storage is used

Troubleshooting
Issue: Login fails
Username must be exactly admin

Password must be exactly admin123

Issue: OTP doesn't work
Check the hint box that displays the OTP

OTP is visible on screen — no email required

Click "Resend OTP" to generate a new code

Issue: Charts not displaying
Ensure internet connection for Chart.js CDN

Refresh the page and try again

Issue: Mobile layout issues
Use landscape orientation on phones

Sidebar can be toggled with ☰ button in top bar

Issue: Keyboard shortcuts not working
Shortcuts work only when no input field is focused

Click outside any input field before using shortcuts

